#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;For when one whacking-stick just isnt enough.^reset;

The Grand Armory Mod adds a bunch of new weapon types to random generation all of which use the existing weapon artwork.

Baton - short and quick stick
Cane - medium and quick stick
Club - large, heavy, blunt weapon which stuns
Greataxe - large, heavy, double bladed axe
Greatsword - slightly longer reach than standard broadsword
Mace - light and quick...for a hammer
Quarterstaff - long and quick stick
Shortspear - one handed short-range spear
Armcannon - very fast plasma shot
Longbow - great for hunting
Spellbook - contains arcane magics

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam
######

[h1]For when one whacking-stick just isnt enough.[/h1]

The Grand Armory Mod adds a bunch of new weapon types to random generation all of which use the existing weapon artwork.

Baton - short and quick stick
Cane - medium and quick stick
Club - large, heavy, blunt weapon which stuns
Greataxe - large, heavy, double bladed axe
Greatsword - slower and slightly longer reach than standard broadsword
Mace - light and quick...for a hammer
Quarterstaff - long and quick stick
Shortspear - one handed short-range spear
Armcannon - very fast plasma shot
Longbow - great for hunting
Spellbook - contains arcane magics

Integrated with [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=802382977]Open Armory[/url]!

Compatibility patches for:
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=729480149]Frackin Universe[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593165]x[/url])
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=817468961]Melee Aiming[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593261]x[/url])
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=760396113]Manufacturer's Touch[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593363]x[/url])
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=780877247]Quarterstaff Armory[/url] ([url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=837593510]x[/url])

[url=community.playstarbound.com/threads/124193/]MEGATHREAD[/url]
Alternate downloads can be found on my [url=https://github.com/IsaacHart/sbmod-grandarm/releases/0.3]github.[/url]

